item.description:
Create, update, delete, freeze/unfreeze, complete, and undo-complete operations.

Concurrency: updated_on is required on all mutation requests. If StrictMode = true (opsettings.json ConcurrencyCheck.StrictMode, hot-reloadable) and the DB updated_on is later than the submitted value, the server returns 409.

// Rights check placeholder: requires appropriate right per operation (CRUD, freeze, complete). Rights checks added during .NET code generation.

request.description:
Creates a new ToDo. When a task-source field is present, upsert logic applies:

  - Existing open record + remark already in DB remark → 204 (no body)
  - Existing open record + remark sent differs → append remark, update differing fields → 201 { seq_no }
  - Existing open record + no remark sent → update differing non-task-source fields → 200 { seq_no }
  - No existing open record → new record created → 201 { seq_no }

Task-source fields (travel_pnr_no, seq_no_charges, seq_no_acct_notes, itinerary_no) are immutable after insert.

Auto-injected (do not set manually): tenant_id, company_code, branch_code, user_id, browser_locale, browser_timezone, ip_address.

